Solution:

Approach 1: Sub-query

select max(salary) as SecondHighestSalary from 
Employee where salary < (select max(salary) from Employee);

Note: This solution does not work for Nth Highest Salary
----------------------------------------------------------------

Approach 2: Window Functions

SELECT MAX(salary) AS SecondHighestSalary 
  FROM (SELECT *, DENSE_RANK() OVER(ORDER BY salary DESC) AS RN FROM Employee) t
  WHERE RN = 2
